result:
<a-modal
  title="新建规则"
  :width="640"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
>
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
      <a-form-item
        label="描述"
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
      >
        <a-input v-decorator="['desc', {rules: [{required: true, min: 5, message: '请输入至少五个字符的规则描述！'}]}]" />
      </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
